cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image translation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of a single generator network, which is a common technique in generative adversarial learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces the concept of domain code to control generative tasks, which is a form of explicit modeling and falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments involve working with unpaired datasets, which is a common challenge in graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) research.
